      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been treated with a lot of love? This car is in really solid shape and has been such a joy to drive! It runs beautifully and is perfect for anyone wanting a dependable vehicle that still looks great on the road. It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and is ready for its next adventure. Come check it out and take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
