    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, delivering power through a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut with upgraded bushings and Bilstein dampers, while recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and valve adjustment. While the finish shows minor road wear, the performance envelope is fully intact, offering the tactile steering feedback and linear power delivery synonymous with the M division's golden era.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
